channel.title: Looking for Model/Item Dump
channel.description:
Hey everyone,
I'm on the hunt for a decent Model/Item Dump..
It must have all the New items, and include the item colours, the intarray stuff and all the other crap you need to add models to your client..
(a dump, i believe, is just a long list of items with information on them..)
NOTE: I DO NOT WANT A LINK TO SILABSOFT'S WEBSITE LIST -> IT'S GOT NOTHING TO DO WITH WHAT I'M AFTER!
ALSO NOTE: DON'T SAY "omg, there is no such thing noob!!" CAUSE I KNOW THERE IS. HOW THE HELL WOULD PEOPLE ADD NEW ITEMS TO THEIR CLIENT OTHERWISE?!
just post a download link or something
Thanks for your time.
PS: sorry for the re-post, i just really need one of these..
